instructions: put the plate on top of the charger
put the napkin vertically on top of the plate
put the dinner fork on the left side of the charger, pointing up
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
put the dinner knife to the right of the charger, with the blade pointing left
put the tea spoon to the right of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon to the right of the tea spoon
put the water glass to the top right of the charger
put the wine glass to the right of the water glass
put a second wine glass below the first one
put the coffee cup to the right of the second wine glass
put the bread plate to the top right of the charger
put the butter knife on top of the bread plate, horizontally pointing right
put the dessert fork in between the bread plate and the water glass, pointing to the right
put the dessert spoon below the dessert fork, pointing left
